text: Karim Hossam (born 8 April 1994) is an Egyptian tennis player. Hossam's career high ATP singles ranking is 337, He achieved it on 9 December 2013. Hossam played for Egypt national team at Davis cup in 2013 ,2014 and 2015. == References == == Other websites == * * * Karim Hossam at Davis cup Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Egyptian sportspeople Category:Male tennis players
